data.title: Rhea Perlman wins Emmy
data.meta_description: Title supplied by cataloger.Photograph caption dated September 18, 1989 reads, "Rhea Perlman holds the Emmy she won for best supporting actress in a comedy, 'Cheers.'" The 41st Annual Primetime Emmy Awards were held on September 17, 1989 at the Pasadena Civic Auditorium.
